org.anarres.ipmi.protocol.packet.ipmi

Enum IPMBAddress

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<IPMBAddress>
      • org.anarres.ipmi.protocol.packet.ipmi.IPMBAddress
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<IPMBAddress>, Code.Wrapper

    public enum IPMBAddress
extends Enum<IPMBAddress>
implements Code.Wrapper
    An IPMB address. Introduces a little type-safety to IPMB addresses. Also handles the left-shift for wire encoding.
